msgstr "訂購計劃的 :guilabel:`重複周期`、產品，以及其他資訊，都會自動填寫。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/plans.rst:98
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Sales` dashboard, click :guilabel:`New` to create a new "
